high_descs: Turn around and head toward the wall, then turn right at the fridge and walk towards the stove, take a right at the stove and cross the room and turn left to face the microwave
Open the microwave and pick up the egg that is on the left then close the microwave
Turn left and walk towards to stove then hang a left and cross the room to the sink
Place the egg in the sink and turn on the faucet, then turn off the faucet and pick up the egg.
Take a step to your right
Place the egg on the counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a clean egg on a counter

high_descs: Turn left and walk around the kitchen island past the fridge and stove top to the microwave that is on the counter in the far corner.
Open the microwave and take out the brown egg that is leftmost in the microwave.  Close the microwave door.
Walk around the kitchen island, past the stove top and fridge, to the sink.
Put the brown egg into the sink in the front right corner, to the right of the spatula.  Fill the sink with water, then drain the sink.
Take the brown egg out of the sink.
Move slightly to the right of the sink, and place the brown egg onto the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed brown egg onto the counter near the sink.

high_descs: Turn around to your left then head to the microwave across the room
Open the microwave pick up the egg on the left side of the microwave then close the microwave
Turn to your left then head to the sink across the room
Put the egg in the sink and rinse it
Turn to your right then make few steps turn to your left facing the sink counter
Put the egg in front of the plant
anns.task_desc: Put the clean egg on top of the counter

high_descs: Turn left and then right to go around the island and find the microwave.
Take the egg out of the microwave and shut the door.
Turn left to go around the island and find the sink on the right.
Put the egg in the sink, turn the water on and then off. Pick up the egg.
Take the egg and take a step to the right.
Place the egg on the counter in front of the house plant.
anns.task_desc: Rinse an egg and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Walk around the island and go to the microwave.
Take an egg out of the microwave.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Rinse the egg in the sink.
Move to the right a bit.
Put the egg on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed egg on the counter.

high_descs: Walk around the island and go to the microwave.
Take an egg out of the microwave.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Rinse the egg in the sink.
Move slightly to the right.
Put the egg on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked, rinsed egg on the counter.
